          "type": "data",
          "data": {
            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h1 id=\"synthetic-control-placebo-inference-explorer\">Synthetic control \u2014 placebo inference explorer</h1>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Choose the treated market and the launch week. The app rebuilds the synthetic\ncounterfactual from the other markets, then runs the <strong>placebo-in-space</strong> test:\npretend each other market was treated and see whether the real market's gap is\nan outlier. The permutation p-value updates as you move the controls.</span>\n<blockquote>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">Note: only market <strong>dma_00</strong> actually carries a planted +12% campaign effect.\nPick any other market and you should see a <em>non-significant</em> p \u2014 the test's\nspecificity in action.</span>\n</blockquote></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
      "console": []
    },
