            "text/markdown": "<span class=\"markdown prose dark:prose-invert contents\"><h3 id=\"dma_00-launch-week-40\">dma_00, launch week 40</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>pre-period fit RMSE: <strong>2.44</strong> (smaller = more trustworthy synthetic)</li>\n<li>placebo permutation <strong>p = 0.053</strong> \u2192 <strong>significant</strong> at the 0.1 level</li>\n</ul>\n<span class=\"paragraph\">If you picked a market with no real campaign, a low p here would be a <em>false\npositive</em> \u2014 which is why the placebo test, not the gap alone, is the evidence.</span></span>"
          }
        }
      ],
